hu.trigary.iodine.api.player

Class IodinePlayerStateChangedEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • hu.trigary.iodine.api.player.IodinePlayerStateChangedEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IodineEvent

    public final class IodinePlayerStateChangedEvent
extends java.lang.Object
implements IodineEvent
    An event that gets called when the state of a player just changed. In most cases, this is going to be a change from IodinePlayer.State.VANILLA to IodinePlayer.State.MODDED.
